        ],
        [
          "Cardinal Bruce De Guy",
          "The Cardinal of the West and signer of the Code of Milan.  He oversees your monomacy."
        ],
        [
          "Chalupavka",
          "Rival for Archbishop: A monstrous Tzimsce Elder from Peru.  She is said to be a deadly and unstable warrior"
        ],
        [
          "Elivira de Cordoba",
          "A Lasombra Elder, she now leads Cardine Scorso - one of the packs that assaulted the haven of the Lasombra Antediluvean"
        ],
        [
          "Kinyado",
          "The Serpent from the Inquisition.  You remember him in Mexico City, he watched gleefully as the False Hand were thrown on the pyres"
        ],
        [
          "Starting Goals",
          "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        ],
        [
          "Become the Archbishop of San Diego.  Use whatever means necessary to discredit, blackmail or kill your rivals without falling back into infernalism"
